  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984230/extras/a9749f2d6d40142fa586ca81e60b445f.avif?t=1717154142\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>The game is a third-person slasher with RPG elements. Using two swords, a bow, magic and other weapons you must clear three locations of lizards. The more lizards you kill, the stronger your character will become. Destroy them all and free your home!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984230/extras/a64d94c408ae46f673c53f58606c4c2f.avif?t=1717154142\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>👽 The game is based on secret historical documents<br>👽 Varied combat system and weapon selection<br>👽 Ancient Magic: Level up to unlock new spells<br>👽 3D graphics and pleasant soundtrack</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984230/extras/c77d8f75d56cab3e5e8315aa0a8f3cdd.avif?t=1717154142\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><i>WASD - MOVE<br>SPACE - JUMP<br>LEFT MOUSE - ATTACK<br>RIGHT MOUSE - BLOCK<br>R - SWITCH WEAPON<br>1-8 - USE SKILL<br>C - STATUS WINDOW<br>I - INVENTORY<br>K- SKILL TREE<br>Q - CHECK QUEST<br>SHIFT - SPRINT<br>DUBLE TAP (WASD) - DODGE ROLL<br>ESCAPE - PAUSE MENU</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984230/extras/a9749f2d6d40142fa586ca81e60b445f.avif?t=1717154142\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>The game is a third-person slasher with RPG elements. Using two swords, a bow, magic and other weapons you must clear three locations of lizards. The more lizards you kill, the stronger your character will become. Destroy them all and free your home!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984230/extras/a64d94c408ae46f673c53f58606c4c2f.avif?t=1717154142\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>👽 The game is based on secret historical documents<br>👽 Varied combat system and weapon selection<br>👽 Ancient Magic: Level up to unlock new spells<br>👽 3D graphics and pleasant soundtrack</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984230/extras/c77d8f75d56cab3e5e8315aa0a8f3cdd.avif?t=1717154142\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><i>WASD - MOVE<br>SPACE - JUMP<br>LEFT MOUSE - ATTACK<br>RIGHT MOUSE - BLOCK<br>R - SWITCH WEAPON<br>1-8 - USE SKILL<br>C - STATUS WINDOW<br>I - INVENTORY<br>K- SKILL TREE<br>Q - CHECK QUEST<br>SHIFT - SPRINT<br>DUBLE TAP (WASD) - DODGE ROLL<br>ESCAPE - PAUSE MENU</i>",
